 "object": "Measured kappa of the remaining Q input (grande_finale.tex thm:q-implies-sp max-fiber form: max_z N_w(z) <= kappa*Fbar, Fbar=C(n,m)|B|^{-w}, after quotient-pulled-back and planted strata are removed; kappa=e^{o(n)} asymptotically per thm:moment-q, explicit finite budgets per prop:q-exact-target/def:q-row-atom). R_prim = |B|^w * max_z |Fib_prim(z)| / C(n,m) is the measured kappa at an exact row, with |B|=p, m=a_+=n/2+w (list route K=n/2). Fib_prim removes quotient/coeff-scale members (lem:coeff-scale, thm:coeff-quotient-extract); R_prim_np additionally removes planted-core strata (thm:head-flatness). R_prim >= R_prim_np is the conservative upper proxy.",
